        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1211843155" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7401944076405988379">Sometimes I read sad books about lonely people and it makes me feel <i>things. </i>It’s so inexplicable and consuming. I’m afraid I’m going to drown with all these sentiments inside me.<br/><br/><b>That’s what I felt reading The Piper’s Son.</b><br/><br/>I don’t know how Melina Marchetta manages to do it, but she always impart something life jarring message to her readers. <br/><br/>Review to come.<br/></span>

